cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.SE 

This paper is primarily focused on characterizing deep learning training workloads, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of software frameworks such as TensorFlow and PyTorch (cs.SE), as well as the application of deep learning in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also involves analyzing the performance of hardware configurations, which could fall under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
